{"tid":2367982,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國政府宣布取消所有入境豁免隔離 下周一起所有入境人士必須進行10天的隔離","createTime":"2021-01-15T18:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T21:35:47.000Z","uid":28114,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8df9f3002b24bfd05dacda3d7f3a14e57e8eef2","tid":2367982,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T18:48:25.000Z","msg":"《英國入境隔離和病毒報告最新措施》<br />\n<br />\n英國政府剛宣布由下周一起，取消所有入境豁免隔離的國家和地區的政策，意味所有入境人士入境後必須進行10天的隔離，除非在五天後獲得陰性的測試報告。所有入境人士出發前，亦必須出示72小時內的陰性的測試報告。<br />\n<br />\n由於巴西應對變種的問題，英政府同時向南美洲及葡萄牙發出旅遊禁令，禁示該地區旅客入境。<br />\n<br />\n首相Boris Johnson宣布，新措施至少維持至2月15日為止。<br />\n<br />\n自夏季推行旅遊通道（travel corridor)政策以來，香港一直是豁免地區。換句話說，由周一起計劃返英的留學生，打算趕搭LOTR尾班車的人士，都會受新措施影響。計劃在1月31日後，在港申請BNO Visa的人士，則必須密切留意2月15日後的政策變化。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：Covid: UK to close all travel corridors from Monday <a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-55681861\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-55681861&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=d21f65d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-55681861</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/297485071746526/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101138131381222%2Fposts%2F297485071746526%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFgwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=9f2895dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/297485071746526/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"734971769e926159221b12bad7b381c2a0f0d5dc","tid":2367982,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67423511a8d0815fe57c38bcf7c6f95a719c92d6","tid":2367982,"uid":128438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8df9f3002b24bfd05dacda3d7f3a14e57e8eef2"